Class Part

  • java.lang.Object
    • meico.xml.AbstractXmlSubtree
      • meico.mpm.elements.Part

  • public class Part
extends AbstractXmlSubtree
    This class interfaces the part-specific information, as opposed to global information that apply to all parts.
